=== Iteration 10 === Sun Feb 22 18:49:10 PST 2026
## Summary

**Completed: Phase 8 ŌĆö Build admin CLI for seeding profiles by ORCID ID list**

### What was built
- **`src/cli/seed-profiles.ts`** ŌĆö Admin CLI tool for seeding researcher profiles from ORCID IDs
- **`src/cli/__tests__/seed-profiles.test.ts`** ŌĆö 25 tests covering all CLI logic

### How it works
```bash
npm run seed -- 0000-0002-1234-5678                    # Single ORCID
npm run seed -- 0000-0002-1234-5678 0000-0003-4567-8901  # Multiple
npm run seed -- --file researchers.txt                   # From file
npm run seed -- --file researchers.txt --skip-deep-mining # Faster seeding
npm run seed -- --dry-run 0000-0002-1234-5678            # Validate only
```

### Key design decisions
- **Reuses existing `seedProfiles()` service** ŌĆö no business logic duplication; CLI handles parsing, progress display, and result formatting
- **File format**: one ORCID per line, `#` comments and blank lines ignored
- **Deduplicates** input ORCID IDs automatically
- **Exit code 1** on pipeline failures for scripting/automation
- **Helper functions exported** (`parseArgs`, `loadOrcidsFromFile`, `validateOrcids`, `formatResults`) for testability

### Test results
- All **1116 tests pass** across 60 test suites (including 25 new CLI tests)
- No TypeScript errors in new files

